summary:
I am a motivated, warm and enthusiastic adult English teacher. The rapport that I have with students and the positive energy that I bring into the classroom helps create an energised learning environment. Being able to help students improve their English really inspires me. After successfully completing my CELTA training course, I knew this is what I wanted to do.
I have developed myself by working in International environments where I have adapted and applied myself well. The opportunity to combine my previous financial, sales and marketing background plus that of teaching, really appeals to me.
